SearchActivity - Class in com.example.yanghanwen.taskmanagementmonster
SearchResultActivity is used for searching a task (or tasks) as a role of provider, it will provide all the tasks and provider is able to either filter tasks to whatever he want through four different status, and can also search a task(s) by entering keywords of username.
